Mgr
mysql [-h slc11fsp.us.oracle.com] -uroot -p

启动服务 service mysqld start
版本：mysql –V；或者select version();
Tables：show databases/tables;

查看表结构
desc table_name;
Show DDl: show create table ld_cart;

indexs
Show: show index from fund_history\G;
Create: create index idx_fund_name on fund(name);








